summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5973 for the improvement of West Kenyon Street from 34th Avenue Southwest to 39th Avenue Southwest; and certain other streets and avenues, by constructing concrete sidewalks and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 79939, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
